---
import InfrastructureMap from '../components/infrastructure/InfrastructureMap.astro';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import OperationFlow from '../components/OperationFlow.astro';
import LiveDemo from '../components/LiveDemo.astro';
import FAQ from '../components/FAQ.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import ChatBubble from '../components/ChatBubble.astro';
import TractionPipeline from '../components/TractionPipeline.astro';
const benefits = [
  ['-68%', 'Tempo de Resposta', 'Eliminação do tempo de espera fora do horário comercial, atendendo o lead no pico exato de interesse.'],
  ['+3.4x', 'Qualificação de Intenção', 'Coleta estruturada de nome, cargo, dor e histórico de conversação antes do handoff.'],
  ['100%', 'Rastreabilidade Comercial', 'Integração total de dados de origem entre captura, CRM e Meta CAPI sem perda de sinais.']
];
---
<Layout title="Agent SDR IA · Operação Plug & Play | neoflowoff.agency" description="Agent SDR IA, página, captura de leads, qualificação, handoff humano e Meta CAPI conectados na Operação SDR IA Plug & Play implantada pela neoflowoff.agency.">
  <div class="page-shell"><Header /><main><Hero />
    <section class="section problem depth-acid-noise"><span class="kicker">01 / O PROBLEMA REAL</span><div class="problem-grid"><h2>O lead chegou.<br /><em>A operação é que não estava pronta para recebê-lo.</em></h2><div class="scene reveal"><p>A campanha gera uma mensagem.<br />A pessoa pergunta preço.<br />Alguém demora para responder.</p><p>Quando o comercial assume, já não sabe de onde ela veio, qual anúncio iniciou a conversa ou o que ela realmente queria.</p><strong>O problema não é apenas gerar leads. É conseguir agir enquanto ainda existe intenção.</strong></div></div></section>
    <OperationFlow />
    <section class="section benefits light-section"><div class="section-head"><span class="kicker">03 / IMPACTO</span><h2>O comercial deixa de<br /><em>começar do zero.</em></h2></div><div class="benefit-grid">{benefits.map(([metric, title,copy],i)=><article class="reveal"><span>0{i+1}</span><h3><span class="mono code-accent">{metric}</span> {title}</h3><p>{copy}</p></article>)}</div></section>
    <LiveDemo />
    <TractionPipeline class="section-divider-pipeline" />
    <InfrastructureMap />
    <section class="section proof"><span class="kicker">07 / PROVA OPERACIONAL</span><div class="proof-grid"><h2>O atendimento na página não é apenas conceito.<br /><em>É a própria arquitetura em ação.</em></h2><div><p>O mesmo sistema utilizado para receber esta conversa faz parte da infraestrutura aplicada pela neoflowoff.agency em páginas, agentes, dados e fluxos comerciais. Status atual da arquitetura:</p><div class="proof-tags">{['Landing: operacional','Agente: operacional','Captura: a validar','Persistência: a validar','Handoff: a validar','Meta CAPI: a validar'].map(x=><span>{x}</span>)}</div></div></div></section>
    <FAQ />
  </main><Footer /></div>
  <ChatBubble />
  <script>
    import { setupClientSideSessionTracking } from '../lib/session-handler';
    setupClientSideSessionTracking();
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver(es => es.forEach(e => { if (e.isIntersecting) e.target.classList.add('visible') }), { threshold: .12 });
    document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(e => observer.observe(e));
  </script>
</Layout>
<style is:global>
.section {
  padding: 120px 7vw;
  position: relative;
}
.eyebrow i, .final-signal i {
  display: inline-block;
  width: 7px;
  height: 7px;
  background: var(--acid);
  border-radius: 50%;
  box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--acid);
  margin-right: 8px;
}
.kicker {
  font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', 'Courier New', monospace;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: .15em;
  color: var(--orange);
  text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 153, 64, 0.45);
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  background: transparent !important;
  padding: 0 !important;
  border: none !important;
  border-radius: 0 !important;
  opacity: 0.4;
  transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
}
.kicker:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}
.kicker::before {
  content: ">_ ";
  color: inherit !important;
  text-shadow: inherit !important;
  margin-right: 6px;
  font-weight: 600;
}
.hero h1, .section h2 {
  font-family: Space Grotesk, sans-serif;
  letter-spacing: -.055em;
  line-height: .96;
  margin: 28px 0;
  font-weight: 500;
}
h1 span, h2 em {
  color: var(--acid);
  font-style: normal;
}
.section-head {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 50px;
}
.section h2 {
  font-size: clamp(40px, 4.8vw, 69px);
}
.section-head .kicker {
  padding-top: 15px;
}
.problem-grid, .proof-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.15fr .85fr;
  gap: 8vw;
}
.scene {
  padding-top: 30px;
}
.scene p {
  font-size: 18px;
  color: #b7bcb4;
  margin: 0 0 26px;
}
.scene strong {
  display: block;
  border-left: 2px solid var(--orange);
  padding-left: 20px;
  font-size: 16px;
}
.benefit-grid h3 {
  font: 500 26px Space Grotesk;
  margin: 55px 0 14px;
}
.benefit-grid p, .proof p {
  color: var(--muted);
}
.benefit-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 18px;
  margin-top: 70px;
}
.benefit-grid article {
  padding: 30px;
  background: var(--panel);
  border-top: 1px solid #394033;
}
.benefit-grid span {
  color: var(--acid);
  font-size: 10px;
}
.final-cta > small {
  display: block;
  color: #6f756c;
  font-size: 11px;
  margin-top: 15px;
  text-align: center;
}
.proof {
  background: #000000;
}
.proof-tags {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 8px;
  margin-top: 35px;
}
.proof-tags span {
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
  background: rgba(255,255,255,.03);
  backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  padding: 9px 12px;
  font-size: 11px;
  color: #b3b8b0;
  transition: all .2s ease;
}
.proof-tags span:hover {
  border-color: rgba(237,255,0,.4);
  background: rgba(237,255,0,.06);
  color: #fff;
}
.final-cta {
  text-align: center;
  padding-top: 140px;
  padding-bottom: 140px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 60%, #EDFF0012, transparent 35%);
}
.final-signal {
  color: var(--muted);
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: .18em;
}
.final-cta p {
  color: var(--muted);
  font-size: 17px;
}
.final-cta .button {
  margin-top: 25px;
}
.light-section {
  background: var(--panel-light);
  color: #a1a1a1;
}
.light-section .eyebrow {
  background: var(--olive);
  color: var(--acid);
  padding: 5px 11px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  display: inline-block;
  font-weight: 600;
}
.light-section .kicker {
  color: #000000 !important;
  text-shadow: none !important;
  opacity: 0.4;
}
.light-section .kicker:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}
.light-section .scene p, .light-section .benefit-grid p {
  color: var(--olive);
}
.light-section .benefit-grid article {
  background: rgba(222, 221, 211, 0.85);
  backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.12);
  color: #000000;
  border-radius: 12px;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.06), inset 0 1px 1px rgba(255,255,255,.6);
  transition: all .3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
}
.light-section .benefit-grid article:hover {
  background: rgba(222, 221, 211, 0.95);
  border-color: var(--orange);
  box-shadow: 
    0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.12), 
    inset 0 1px 1px rgba(255,255,255,.8), 
    0 0 0 1px var(--acid), 
    0 8px 24px rgba(255, 122, 5, 0.15);
  transform: translateY(-4px);
}
.light-section .mono.code-accent {
  font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace;
  background: var(--olive);
  color: var(--acid);
  padding: 4px 8px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  font-size: 0.85em;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-right: 6px;
  display: inline-block;
  vertical-align: middle;
}
.light-section .benefit-grid article span {
  color: var(--olive);
  font-weight: 700;
}
.light-section .scene strong {
  border-left: 2px solid var(--orange);
  color: #000000;
}
.light-section .section-head em, .light-section h2 em {
  color: var(--olive);
}
.reveal {
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(18px);
  transition: .65s ease;
}
.reveal.visible {
  opacity: 1;
  transform: none;
}
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  .reveal {
    opacity: 1 !important;
    transform: none !important;
    transition: none !important;
  }
}
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .section {
    padding: 80px 24px;
  }
  .problem-grid, .proof-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  .section-head {
    display: block;
  }
  .benefit-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
}
@media (max-width: 560px) {
  .section h2 {
    font-size: 39px;
  }
  .problem-grid {
    gap: 5px;
  }
  .final-cta {
    padding: 100px 22px;
  }
  .proof-grid {
    gap: 12px;
  }
}
</style>
